Insider Activity


Individual




Todd M. Abbrecht



Mr. Todd M. Abbrecht is a Managing Director at Thomas H. Lee Partners LP. He is on the Board of Directors at Fogo de Chão, Inc., Party City Holdings, Inc., Party City Holdco, Inc., inVentiv Health, Inc., Aramark, Intermedix Corp., Fogo de Chão Ltda., and Curo Health Services LLC.
Mr. Abbrecht was previously employed as a Principal by Credit Suisse First Boston and a Principal by National Waterworks Holdings, Inc. He also served on the board at Warner Chilcott Plc, Dunkin' Brands, Inc., and Michael Foods Group, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from The Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania and an MBA from Harvard Business School.



